## Database Migrations

```bash
# Migrations run automatically during deploy
# To run manually:
kamal app exec 'bin/rails db:migrate'

# Check migration status
kamal app exec 'bin/rails db:migrate:status'

# Rollback migration
kamal app exec 'bin/rails db:rollback'
```

